name: Barobisha Satsang Vihar
history:
Sree Sree Borda, Puj. Ranga maa, Rev. Suntida visited on 23.03.1974. Acharyadev Sree Sree Dada, Rev. Baro Baudi, Rev. Babaida in 2003 & 2005. Rev. Bordidi, Acharyadev Sree Sree Dada, Rev. Baro Baudi stayed one night on 31.05.2010.
Rev. Mejda, Rev. Suntida, Rev. Sejda, Rev. Sipaida, Rev. Binkida, Rev. Subhada, Rev. Tinkuda and many others of Thakur Family visited the place several times. Inaugurated by Rev. Binkida on 29.05.2009.
